</a>。该唱片是继 Kings Of Leon 于 2021 年发行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kings-of-leon-when-you-see-yourself-review-2894039">《When You See Yourself》</a>之后发行的。</p><p>其他新闻方面，Kings Of Leon 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-live-at-wrexham-bonus-version-of-new-album-3751422">宣布了他们即将发行的专辑的附赠版本，其中将包括他们 2023 年在雷克瑟姆举行的大型演出中的现场曲目</a>。您可以<a href="https://uk.kingsofleonshop.com/products/can-we-please-have-fun-wrexham-live-edition-2cd-can-we-please-have-fun-wrexham-live-edition-dual-colour-cassette-signed-art-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里了解更多信息并购买</a>。</p><p>他们还计划于今年晚些时候开始一系列<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-further-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3591919">英国/爱尔兰</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-2024-world-tour-dates-in-london-and-north-america-3591521">北美巡演</a>，其中包括在伦敦<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST 海德公园 2024</a>举行的头条表演。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/kings-of-leon-tickets/artist/862453?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHUuy3%3AiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此查找任何剩余门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caleb-followill-on-why-he-didnt-want-sex-on-fire-to-be-on-only-by-the-night-3754088">Caleb Followill 的帖子解释了为什么他不希望“Sex On Fire”出现在“Only By The Night”节目中，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
